Bvlgari BLV Eau de Parfum II 1.7 fl oz
description: Bring a subtle yet sophisticated scent to your casual lifestyle with BLV II by Bvlgari. This women's fragrance features a combination of star anise, mandarin, patchouli, vetiver, licorice, and musk mixed with a number of other notes to provide you with a scent that can be worn in a variety of situations. Whether you choose to wear it at a family event or a fun outing with your closest friends, this is the right perfume for you.

name: Dolce & Gabbana The One Gentleman 1.6 fl oz
description: The One Gentleman, an exciting men's fragrance by Dolce & Gabbana, is great for casual wear for a day spent at the office or an exciting night out with someone special. Introduced in 2010, The One layers spicy top notes of pepper and cardamom over tones of fennel, lavender, and a subtle patchouli. The fragrance medley is rounded out by a heady vanilla base note which holds the entire melange together.

name: Givenchy Pour Homme  Blue Label 1.7 fl oz
description: A resonant and enticing scent for men that radiates casual sophistication for any time of day, Givenchy Blue Label for men is an evocative, fruity but manly fragrance that will turn heads wherever you travel. Introduced by renowned style icon Givenchy in 2004, Givenchy Blue Label combines vetiver, hedione, grapefruit, bergamot, cedar and pepper in a thoughtful construction that's perfect for the contemporary man. It's an evocative fragrance that works just as well for a night on the town with the guys as for a quiet dinner for two.

name: Light Blue Living Stromboli by Dolce & Gabbana 2.5 fl oz
description: In 2012, Dolce & Gabbana introduced the men's cologne Light Blue Living Stromboli Pour Homme, a fragrance that combines aquatic, fresh, citrus, aromatic, and spicy notes to create a crisp, refreshing scent. This is a casual scent great for everyday use, and it has great staying power. Splash some on each morning before you head to work and you'll feel instantly uplifted and invigorated, or spray a little on after an intense workout at the gym to quickly freshen up.

name: Heat Rush by Beyonce 3.4 fl oz
description: Heat Rush by Beyonce is a perfume made with the casual woman in mind. Introduced in 2011, this fragrance contains a mix of passion fruit sorbet, Brazilian cherry and blood orange combined with mango blossom, orange hibiscus and yellow tiger orchid. The result is an exciting perfume that is the perfect match for a number of occasions. No matter where you choose to wear Heat Rush, it is sure to make heads turn the moment you walk through the door.

name: Heat by Beyonce 3.4 fl oz
description: Beyonce Heat is a sensual daytime perfume for women. The international star Beyonce introduced this fragrance in 2010, and it has quickly established itself as an excellent everyday perfume. This fragrance beautifully combines notes of sequoia milkwood, almond macaroon, blush peach, creme de musk, red vanilla, and honeysuckle nectar. The result is a fragrance that is subtle enough for everyday use, while being noticeable enough to leave an impression.

name: Pink Friday by Nicki Minaj 1.7 fl  oz
description: You'll feel like a rock goddess when you wear this sultry, sweet scent from the design house of Nicki Minaj. Designed to embody the energy and alluring appeal of rap star Nicki Minaj, Pink Friday was launched in 2012 and features an intoxicating blend of florals and woods. With opening top notes of Italian mandarin, blackberry, and star fruit, followed by darker base notes of musk, vanilla, and carmelized pear, it's easy to get lost in this dreamy, casual scent for her.

name: 212 Men by Carolina Herrara 1 fl oz
description: Introduced in 1999, 212 for Men by Carolina Herrera captures the spirit of New York. It elegantly combines woody, floral, and musky notes in a distinctively energetic bouquet. Top notes of mandarin and grapefruit are underpinned by sandalwood and iron woods. A gentle spice ties the fragrance together, giving the wearer a sensual and alluring scent. It exudes the stylish aroma of refinement appropriate for all daytime activities. This sophisticated bottle truly matches the cologne inside.

name: Bvlgari Aqua Marine Pour Homme 3 pc set
description:
A resonant and enticing scent for men that emanates casual chic for any time of day or night, Bvlgari Aqua Marine is a fruity but very manly fragrance that will turn heads wherever you travel. Introduced by Bvlgari in 2008, Aqua Marine combines notes of pine needle, cedar wood, rosemary flower, neroli bigarade and grapefruit in a construction that's perfect for the contemporary man. This versatile cologne works well for hitting the town with buddies or having a quiet dinner with that special someone.

Set Includes Spray 1.7 fl oz, After shave 2.5 fl oz, Shampoo/Shower Gel 2.5 fl oz

name: Lacoste Elegance 1.6 Fl Oz
description: A casual scent for men, Lacoste Elegance cologne is a wonderfully evocative fragrance that balances a moderate, woodsy essence with a complex variety of notes. First introduced by Lacoste in 2007, this fragrance has a thoughtful construction that expertly blends notes of chocolate, thyme, spicy heart and mandarin zest in perfect balance. Fresh and clean while remaining hearty and very masculine, Lacoste Elegance is great for a broad variety of excursions, including a day out with friends or a relaxed coffee date.
